[command] | bc

Stdin:
    command    input command

cat <file>

Arguments:
    file       input file

cd <path>

Arguments:
    path       destination path

chmod <readperm> <writeperm> <folder>

Arguments:
    readperm   read permission 0 - 4
    writeperm  write permission 0 - 4
    folder     folder

clear

cp <file|folder> <folder>

Arguments:
    file       source file
    folder     source folder
    folder     destination folder

curl [-L] [-O] [-f] <url>

Flags:
    -L         follow redirects
    -O         save to file
    -f         fail silently

Arguments:
    url        destination url

