read [-p <msg>] <var>

Flags:
    -p <msg>   message to display when getting input

Arguments:
    var        variable to save user input

rm [-r] [-f] [--no-preserve-root] <folder>

Flags:
    -r         delete recursively
    -f         force delete
    -no-preserve-root do not preserve root directory

Arguments:
    folder     target folder

sleep <time|times|timem|timems>

Arguments:
    time       sleep time in seconds
    time(s)    sleep time in seconds
    time(m)    sleep time in minutes
    time(ms)   sleep time in milliseconds

stat <folder>

Arguments:
    folder     target folder

sudo [-s] <command>

Flags:
    -s         enter root user

Arguments:
    command    command to execute

sync

